COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 608, L.D. 1493
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment replaces the bill and changes the title. The amendment further restricts
33 the allowable uses of the visual media production reimbursement and credit by precluding
44 the use of the reimbursement and credit for the production of advertisements and for
55 productions produced primarily for industrial, corporate or institutional purposes or for
66 internal use.
77 FISCAL NOTE REQUIRED
88 (See attached)
